nail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F000537_af4671375987879b8ae20dffd73214da.jpg&h=1a83c7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經冇咩點見到佢地了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔見左好多成員 應該知驚 佢地冇再嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc1b362434d7787c9c9373f741652bffec5c142","tid":205012,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"點解無聽過會叫<br />\n而家先知原來識叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6816d3b4303d7ddb4f869ab0dcf91e165edcd0a8","tid":205012,"uid":68908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T23:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答你 我屋企都養左佢地10幾年 直到佢地嘈到啲叫聲 係可以叫醒我 就頂唔順想抄佢地家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前老豆係街市買 第一次捉我擺左係佢日日都經過嘅位 去食飯食食下聽到聲 捉住左係度掙扎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就開曬黎用 全部都捉到 用曬就係淘寶買 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/000537_af4671375987879b8ae20dffd73214da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F000537_af4671375987879b8ae20dffd73214da.jpg&h=1a83c7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經冇咩點見到佢地了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔見左好多成員 應該知驚 佢地冇再嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed0bf96c8e7d7dbb0cdc83408fdfe9444562f0a","tid":205012,"uid":54081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"簷蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}